FROM encounters e 
LEFT JOIN claims_encounters ce ON ce.encounter = e.id 
LEFT JOIN claims c ON c.id = ce.claim 
LEFT JOIN payers p ON p.id = c.payer

question: Please provide me the number of procedures uncovered by the payer Dual Eligible.
answers:
SELECT 
  COUNT (DISTINCT transact.procedurecode) AS uncovered_procedures
FROM 
  payers 
  LEFT JOIN payer_transitions AS pt 
  ON pt.payer = payers.id 
  LEFT JOIN claims AS claim 
  ON pt.patient = claim.patient 
  LEFT JOIN claims_transactions transact 
  ON claim.id = transact.claim 
WHERE 
  payers.name = 'Dual Eligible' 
AND NOT transact.submittedforpayment
